This is my captstone project that my team of three student researchers produced for the Bridges to Healthcare Technology Program under Carnegie Mellon University and UnitedHealth Group. We aimed to explore and understand the influences on teen birth rates by analyzing county-level data to reach actionable insights and a reccomendation for UHG.
